subject: From the UBS Swiss bank CEO , Mr. Sergio Ermotti
body:
Attn: Mr Walter

This is to officially notify you that we have been waiting for your partner
Mr. Russell Robinson  to get back to us so that we can immediately complete
the fund valued USD$45Million ATM card
handover delivery to your nominated address.

Furthermore , be informed that a deadline payment cancellation has been
approved been 25th of February 2024 and any failure to complete
balance fee on or before the deadline your payment ATM Card handover
delivery process will be cancelled.

In this regards, you are advise to get back to me as quickly as possible so
that further directives will be given to you to offset the balance fee via
Bitcoin transfer to our agent wallet account  or via
bank wire transfer to our agent account .

I attached here my I'd card for your record.

I hope the above details information is made clear while i wait for
your immediate response.

Yours in service
Sergio Ermotti
Chief Executive officer
UBS BANK GROUP UBS PRIVATE
